Name: Enduring Dreamers™: Freya
About the game: …even the greatest of adventures have but a small beginnings. ARCADE Endless Platform Think, plan, jump, all while a cold harsh storm forces you forward. Some of the obstacles you will be facing are: Spikes Poisonous flowers Rotating platforms Vertical/horizontal platforms Falling platforms Crushing pillars Flying penguins Breakable ice …with many more obstacles to come! Can you perform this trick? THINGS TO LOOK FORWARD TO Move/re-make the game on a new updated engine. Add additional fun arcade modes. Implement multiplayer for players to play with friends. Thanks for reading, Freya out!
